         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">29/1/92 ¶  ¶ Let me take the earliest opportunity, dear Mr Wilson, to thank the hon. the Chief Secretary and his hon. ministerial colleagues for the generous consideration, shown me in maintaining my ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">92.01.29</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">T92/2768, unit 663, VPRS 3992/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>29/1/92</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Let me take the earliest opportunity, dear Mr Wilson, to thank the hon. the Chief Secretary and his hon. ministerial colleagues for the generous consideration, shown me in maintaining my work and scientific dignity<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to T.Wilson, 27 January 1892.</p>
               </note> and assure them, that I shall just as before give my whole time and thought and income, for maintaining the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">prestige</hi>
               </seg> of the position, which Victoria has throughout maintained in the branch of scientific and applied knowledge, which I represent. As the Department becomes <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">abolished</hi>
               </seg> I presume the £400, mentioned in the Age as working expenses, will be a <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">grant</hi>
               </seg> or allowance, so that the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">cheapest</hi>
               </seg> arrangements can be made to carry on the information, and so that no special transactions need <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">trouble</hi>
               </seg> yourself as my superior officer[.]<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> I will wait on you some evening soon, to thank you personally for the powerful aid, by which I am now able to proceed in my scientific and utilitarian career unimpaired in my honor.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="de">The file contains the following calculations, made by Wilson:</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; text-align: center; "
                     xml:lang="de">Government Botanists Branch</p>
                  <p rend="extra%20space"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 7pt; text-align: end; "
                     xml:lang="de">Present <seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Annual Expenditure</hi>
                     </seg>£Salaries.1,705Contingencies.1,160£2,865</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="de">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[Govt] Branch be abolished, the following payments to be made </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="de">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Gratuities to</hi>
                     </seg> Messrs Luehmann and Minchin who have not attained the age of 60 years non-recurring £<seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">862.6.8</hi>
                     </seg>
                  </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="de">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>(The other Members of the Staff, are not entitled to a gratuity, in consequence of having joined the Service subsequent to the passing of Ramsay's Act.)</p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; text-align: center; "
                     xml:lang="de">Annual</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; text-align: end; "
                     xml:lang="de">Estimated Annual Expenditure for maintaining the Botanic Museum, say500*Pension to Baron von Mueller520£1,020<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>*This, of course, is a mere guess. I presume the present Museum will have to be maintained somewhere and possibly the collection added to as heretofore</p>
                  <p rend="valediction"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">T.R.W.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation in an unknown hand: 'Present cost £2865 Barons Salary 800 Pension 520'. On 28 January 1892 the Chief Secretary, A. McLean, minuted: 'Mueller to be [retained] Total cost to be [...] £[1700] per annum [...] in writing.' <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">several words indistinct - check MS.</seg>
                  </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>There is also a note by McLean dated 31/12/91: </seg>'abolish office &amp; give 3 months' notice.' <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">There is also an added note signed GB [George Bell, for Under Secretary] '[…] copy' and dated 28 Jany 1892.</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">where to put this and needs an explanation.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Gratefully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
